		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「豚兽大王」很简单的进行一次上挑，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「豚兽大王」踱步小跑冲了一下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="439" height="258" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「豚兽大王」进行长达15s的蓄力，蓄力完成后，进行连续3次的冲撞，每次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">300%</span><span>伤害。<br/>需要累计</span><span color="#ffbfbf">2500削韧</span><span>且的攻击方可打断蓄力，中断蓄力将扣除「豚兽大王」10%生命值；</span><span textDecoration="underline">钝击</span><span>造成的削韧按5倍计入，单次最高计入上限为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">800</span><span>削韧。<br/>以此方法扣除的生命值不致死，生命值低于10%便不再被此机制扣除。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="972" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="359" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">自带霸体。<br/>钝击：如大剑普战终、下落攻击、超载、炸药桶等。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
